{"tid":962932,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"應對外國勢力　周浩鼎輸曾鈺成九條街","createTime":"2018-12-31T08:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T09:21:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd15d5764f0684b170a5985c578a9606814a7926","tid":962932,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T08:46:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181231/20580511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F20580511&d=STMkvUT9Oev8oTGP0AguHDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=ad776920\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F20580511&h=b962b3ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181231/20580511</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月31日 <br />\n<br />\n西環集中營：<br />\n應對外國勢力　周浩鼎輸曾鈺成九條街 - 季陶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181231/large/1546186631_73a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181231%2Flarge%2F1546186631_73a4.jpg&h=49e17fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周浩鼎<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n民主黨早前成立國際關係委員會，由前黨主席劉慧卿任委員會主席，明顯意識到未來一段日子，國際社會將再次提高對香港問題關注，所以先作準備，那建制派又有何應對？有民主派中人指，近日民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎到訪美國，可說是建制派在國際層面，平衡民主派聲音的策略，但有曾與周同場的民主派人指出，周的「戰鬥力」頗一般，他直言面對「外國勢力」，建制陣營最有「殺傷力」的人，非民建聯前主席曾鈺成莫屬。<br />\n<br />\n該民主派中人指，面對「外國勢力」，周浩鼎極其量只是重複官方立場，就如他之前訪美，美國官員主動提及民主派議員被DQ、英國《金融時報》亞洲新聞編輯馬凱被拒續簽證等事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n表現如錄音機<br />\n<br />\n「周浩鼎話佢嘅回應又係搬出乜嘢有依法辦事、『一國兩制』底線不能僭越、港獨同分裂國家行為違反基本法咁，其實同北京、港府官方立場冇分別，根本冇乜說服人哋嘅作用，人哋係想聽作為民選議員嘅觀點，唔係北京嘅錄音機」。<br />\n<br />\n他又說當年曾與曾鈺成同場見「外國勢力」，形容曾的「戰鬥力」真的令人開眼界，「曾鈺成好嘢嘅地方，除咗英文好，仲在於佢嗰種講歪理能力，有次見外國議員，佢捉住民主派一點，再左扭右扭講到北京官方立場，好似連民主派都無法反駁」，笑言在座民主派明知他歪理連篇，但一時又不知從何反駁，「事後大家話，要出馬丁（李柱銘）級數，先可以頂到曾主席」。至於同周浩鼎比較，他笑言難以比較，「因為完全唔同層次」。<br />\n<br />\n季陶<br />\n周一、三、五刊出  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳： 微信公眾號元旦上線　中聯辦：權威發佈 (李八方)"},{"pid":"bdca31dfb470836dc697d942b17607e33effc215","tid":962932,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T08:52:11.000Z","msg":"其實而家呢個局<br />\n曾鈺成都扭唔掂啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b84c9fee6feaa1fb9cc2c0befedb458d3a6931","tid":962932,"uid":50428,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T08:54:15.000Z","msg":"主席數學系，logic 同啲傻狗比。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0e725a988c87928b402ef8dbe15d87620766d5","tid":962932,"uid":70301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:34:25.000Z","msg":"根本唔止鳩浩鼎，<br />\n<br />\n根本係全體販民同全體保皇黨都輸老鼠成九條街啦"},{"pid":"0b8d59c0271797c38ca193d8d89f1febae5b6b5d","tid":962932,"uid":203058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:56:56.000Z","msg":"事後大家話，要出馬丁（李柱銘）級數，先可以頂到曾主席」<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦<br />\n馬丁咪又係垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5085e3fc828bae56ef4f1c279f4f539aee41f3ed","tid":962932,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b8d59c0271797c38ca193d8d89f1febae5b6b5d","tid":962932,"uid":203058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05: